ExcelFileNotFoundException - Exception in com.ab.exceptions
The ExcelFileNotFoundException class extends the InvalidFilePathException class to represent an exception that occurs when the Excel file is not found at the specified path.

ExcelReadException - Exception in com.ab.exceptions
The ExcelReadException class extends the FrameworkExceptions class to represent an exception that occurs when an error occurs while reading an Excel file.
ExcelReadException(String) - Constructor for exception com.ab.exceptions.ExcelReadException
This constructor takes a message as input and passes it to the constructor of the FrameworkExceptions class.
ExcelUtil - Class in com.ab.utilities

ExtentReport - Class in com.ab.reports
The ExtentReport class is used to initialize and close the ExtentReports instance, create and manage test reports, and add information such as authors and suites to the report.
ExtentReportLogger - Class in com.ab.reports
The ExtentReportLogger class provides methods to log test step results to an ExtentTest object in the test report.
ExtentReportManager - Class in com.ab.reports
